revisions.description: New element was added to support Memory Utilization per module display. The New Mib Object is genMemUtilizationTable that presents per module Physical Ram and Percentage of used memory - designed by P. Spector

MBytes.name: MBytes
MBytes.description: Storage size, expressed in units of megabytes.

genCpuUtilizationTable.name: genCpuUtilizationTable
genCpuUtilizationTable.description: A list of CPU utilization entries.

genCpuIndex.name: genCpuIndex
genCpuIndex.description: An index that uniquely identifies the CPU.

genCpuUtilizationEnableMonitoring.name: genCpuUtilizationEnableMonitoring
genCpuUtilizationEnableMonitoring.description: Enable or disable CPU utilization monitoring. The default is disabled(1).

genCpuUtilizationEnableEventGeneration.name: genCpuUtilizationEnableEventGeneration
genCpuUtilizationEnableEventGeneration.description: Enable or disable event generation for CPU utilization. The default is disable (1).

genCpuUtilizationHighThreshold.name: genCpuUtilizationHighThreshold
genCpuUtilizationHighThreshold.description: The high threshold of CPU utilization in percentage, which can be from 50% to 99%. If event generation is enabled while the utilization is above the threshold, an event will be generated. The default value of this threshold is 95%. No event will be generated when the utilization crosses below the high threshold.

genCpuAverageUtilization.name: genCpuAverageUtilization
genCpuAverageUtilization.description: The curent average CPU utilization in percentage if the monitoring is enabled and full window of results has been captured. Sample window is 60 seconds. Number of samples is 12, which results a sample interval of 5 seconds.

genCpuCurrentUtilization.name: genCpuCurrentUtilization
genCpuCurrentUtilization.description: The current CPU utilization in percentage if the monitoring is enabled. The sample interval is 5 seconds.

genCpuUtilizationHistoryTable.name: genCpuUtilizationHistoryTable
genCpuUtilizationHistoryTable.description: A list of CPU utilization history entries.

genCpuUtilizationHistoryEntry.name: genCpuUtilizationHistoryEntry
genCpuUtilizationHistoryEntry.description: A collection of CPU utilization history.

genCpuUtilizationHistorySampleIndex.name: genCpuUtilizationHistorySampleIndex
genCpuUtilizationHistorySampleIndex.description: An index that uniquely identifies the particular sample. This index starts at 1 and increases by one as each new sample is taken.

genCpuHistoryUtilization.name: genCpuHistoryUtilization
genCpuHistoryUtilization.description: The cpu utiliztion in percentage of a particular sample. The number of samples is 12, which results in a sample interval of 5 seconds. The sample window is 60 seconds.

genMemUtilizationTotalRAM.name: genMemUtilizationTotalRAM
genMemUtilizationTotalRAM.description: The total size of the ram in MBytes.

genMemUtilizationOperationalImage.name: genMemUtilizationOperationalImage
genMemUtilizationOperationalImage.description: The total size of the operational image in Bytes.

genMemUtilizationDynAllocMemUsed.name: genMemUtilizationDynAllocMemUsed
genMemUtilizationDynAllocMemUsed.description: The dynamically allocated memory has been used in Bytes.

genMemUtilizationDynAllocMemMaxUsed.name: genMemUtilizationDynAllocMemMaxUsed
genMemUtilizationDynAllocMemMaxUsed.description: The dynamically allocated memory has been used maximally in Bytes.

genMemUtilizationDynAllocMemAvailable.name: genMemUtilizationDynAllocMemAvailable
genMemUtilizationDynAllocMemAvailable.description: The available dynamically allocated memory in Bytes.

genMemUtilizationAllocationFailures.name: genMemUtilizationAllocationFailures
genMemUtilizationAllocationFailures.description: The total number of the memory that fails allocation.

genMemUtilizationSysRAMNotificationHighW.name: genMemUtilizationSysRAMNotificationHighWaterMark
genMemUtilizationSysRAMNotificationHighW.description: The high water mark for ram allocation in Bytes. If this value has been exceeded, a trap will be generated. This value can't be higher than Total System RAM.

genMemUtilizationTable.name: genMemUtilizationTable
genMemUtilizationTable.description: Memory Utilization by module in stack or blade in modular solution

genMemUtilizationEntry.name: genMemUtilizationEntry
genMemUtilizationEntry.description: Memory Utilization Table indexed by Module ID

genMemUtilizationPhyRam.name: genMemUtilizationPhyRam
genMemUtilizationPhyRam.description: The total size of the physical ram in Bytes.
